txt.en: 'Even the farmhouses just outside of town were not exempt from the Orc-raiders...they burned everything. All of the Eastemnet is suffering from the attacks, and food is short everywhere. If we are to survive, we must be able to provide for ourselves, and that means the farms must be rebuilt.'
'Hytbold is one step closer to being rebuilt and restored.'
Farmhouse of the Entwash Vale: Rebuild
